description:
&lt;p&gt;Our chemotherapy nursing team in our Warwickshire Hospital currently have an opportunity for a Chemotherapy Nurse to join us on bank.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nuffield Health Warwickshire Hospital &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Nuffield Health Warwickshire Hospital offers the latest facilities and technology for the care of patients from Leamington Spa, Coventry, Kenilworth, Stratford and surrounding areas with a wide range of surgical and medical requirements.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Our specialities include orthopaedics, spinal surgery, eye care, oncology, diagnostic imaging and general surgery. We have made this hospital available to NHS trusts to support patients with the COVID-19 (coronavirus) outbreak, cancer and other urgent health conditions. We are open for new referrals and are offering online consultations to our patients, working with the NHS to determine the most clinically appropriate diagnostic tests or procedures to carry out at this time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Whether you join us from the NHS or a private setting, we will give you the greatest opportunities to fulfil your passion for nursing and grow your career. You will have the chance to inspire others to deliver the highest standards of patient care.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;As part of our bank you will work in a friendly Oncology unit, as a Bank Chemotherapy Nurse you will:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Administer Chemotherapy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assist consultants during Clinics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support patients through their Cancer Journey&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Person&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;To succeed as an Chemotherapy Bank Nurse you will need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To have or be working towards a Chemotherapy Qualification and Experience and it would advantageous to have experience of Oncology Nursing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To work flexible hours to suit the department Monday to Friday&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be an excellent communicator and team worker – flexible and motivated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RGN or equivalent qualification&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Has or working towards a university accredited chemotherapy course and experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Staff are continually supported to develop with training&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Holiday in line with the Working Time Directive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Access to our Pension Scheme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Discounted gym membership at £15.00 a month that they need to set up directly with the club. Discount does not extend to partners and family members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Be your best and join us in building a healthier nation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary - £16 - £22  per hour (Depending on Experience)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location - Leamington Spa, Warwickshire&lt;br /&gt;Closing date - 11/11/2020&lt;br /&gt;Contract Type - Bank&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Working on the bank means you are not contracted to a set number of hours per week but instead work on an ad-hoc basis to suit the needs of the business and your availability.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Applications will be considered as they are received and interviews will be arranged accordingly. We reserve the right to close adverts early, for example, where we have received an unprecedented high volume of applications. Therefore please apply early to ensure you are considered for the post. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
